 together without requiring changes to thesoftware.&quot;andP;  Straighten out whether telcos are regulated or competitive --that will influence what they do.'andM;*  We are at square one when it comes to m aging networks that go betweencountries.&quot;andM;* Digital systems will be out of vogue in about 15 years.andP;  The research labsare looking at new analog system ...&quot;(Oy vey!!!)andO;</TEXT></DOC>